name: COLDACT NEW Capsule 20
description: COLDACT CAPSULE is a combination of Phenylephrine and Chlorpheniramine which belongs to the group of medicines called Nasal decongestants and Antihistamines respectively.

name: JinCold Capsule 20
description: Zincold Tablet is a combination medicine that effectively relieves symptoms of common cold such as blocked nose, runny nose, watery eyes, sneezing, and congestion or stuffiness. It helps to loosen thick mucus, making it easier to cough out. This makes it easier for air to move in and out.

name: Himalaya Tulsi Syrup
description: Himalaya Tulasi Syrup helps suppress cough and aids the mobilization of mucus. It assists in calming and dilating the lung's airways providing relief.

name: Aayudh Syrup
description: It is made using a variety of natural herbs with antiviral and immunity boosting properties that makes it helpful in case of viral infections and to increase the body's immunity. It is beneficial in viral and bacterial infections, sore throat, cough and cold, flu, etc., with antioxidant and immunomodulatory properties.

name: Crocin tablet
description: It is used to reduce fever and treat mild to moderate pain. Also, it is used to relieve headache, migraine, toothache.

name: Cofsils
description: Cofsils cough syrup is a combination medicine containing diphenhydramine, ammonium chloride, and sodium citrate which helps in reducing cough.
